{
  "texts": [
    "Limitations pointed out in this study will be addressed in future work.",
    "The resultant increase in data brought into the dataset by these samples will better generalize across diverse clinical scenarios.",
    "Besides, with advanced architectures using Vision Transformers or hybrid transformer-CNN models, further improvements in feature representation and accuracy will be achieved.",
    "Such efforts will be directed at optimizing DWT and lightweight models for real-time applications in resource-constrained environments.",
    "Conclusively, by wrapping up some hyperparameter optimization automation techniques and with extended external validation on independent datasets, the robustness and scalability of the framework are ensured."
  ]
}